content.c_description: There’s a massive paradigm shift going on in the world of search from chaotic results to verified answers. Today, consumers are asking questions, and they expect answers. We kick off ONWARD19 with a sneak peek at what’s on the road ahead for Yext and what it will take to ensure that your brand is answers-ready.
content.yext/name: ONWARD19 Opening Keynote: Truth Be Told With Howard Lerman
